            //FAQ
            {"titleFAQ1", "How much of my compensation history can I see?" },
            {"descFAQ1", "You can see 3 years of compensation history. Scroll through the list of your paystubs or easily search by date." },
            {"titleFAQ2", "Where can I view my actual check stub or W2?" },
            {"descFAQ2", "You can sign in to www.paycor.com with the same credentials you used for this app to view an actual copy of your check stub or W2." },
            {"titleFAQ3", "How do I punch from the app?" },
            {"descFAQ3", "The app supports mobile punching for companies that have our Perform Time product.  Your company must have this product and enable mobile punching for you to use this feature." },
            {"titleFAQ4", "How do I view my time card or see the total hours I've worked?"},
            {"descFAQ4", "If your company has our Perform Time product and enables mobile punching for their employees, you can view these details by tapping View Time Card Summary on the homepage of our app. You'll see a summary of hours worked for the current week, current pay period, and previous pay period. For more details about your daily punches or time logged, go to paycor.com."},
            {"titleFAQ5", "I forgot to punch in. Can I add a manual punch from the app?"},
            {"descFAQ5", "You'll have to go to paycor.com to add a manual punch. Use the same credentials you use for this app. Sign in and go to Time Card to add a manual punch."},
            {"titleFAQ6", "Can I request time off in the app?"},
            {"descFAQ6", "Yes! If your company has enabled this feature, you can navigate to the Time Off area and tap Request Time Off. Once submitted, we'll send an email to your manager for approval. If you can't see the Request Time Off button, contact your company administrator."},
            {"titleFAQ7", "If I made an error, how do I cancel my time off request?"},
            {"descFAQ7", "You can cancel time off requests that are pending your manager's approval. Tap on the pending request within the Time Off area of the app, then tap Cancel Request."},
            {"titleFAQ8", "Where's my work schedule?" },
            {"descFAQ8", "Our app will display your work schedule if your company has the Perform Time product and you have a schedule available. Talk to your manager or company administrator if you have questions about your schedule." },
            {"titleFAQ9", "How do I suggest a new feature?" },
            {"descFAQ9", "New stuff, we love it too! Inside the navigation menu, tap Feedback and fill in the form to share your thoughts. We review and consider all of your ideas for future updates." },
            {"titleFAQ10", "What if there's an error in my information?" },
            {"descFAQ10", "Please contact your payroll or HR administrator for help." },
            {"titleFAQ11", "Why do I have to sign in when using the app?" },
            {"descFAQ11", "We care about your security and want to protect your personal information. If you’re using an iPhone 5+ or Android 6+, you can enable Touch ID or Fingerprint Authentication to speed up signing in." },

